The '''skill hall''' in a [[player-owned house]] is a room where the player can display various [[skill]] achievements. This room can be created with 25 [[Construction]] and {{Coins|15000}}.
There are 6 [[hotspot]]s available:

*[[Armour space]]
*[[Head trophy space]]
*[[Fishing trophy space]]
*[[Rug space]]
*[[Rune case space]]
*[[Stair space]]

