==Rugs/Stairs==
A staircase added to a skill hall on the ground floor will prompt the player to build it "Up" or "Down". When building an "Up" staircase, then attempting to climb the staircase, the Construction interface will ask if the player want to add a room at the top of the staircase. The rooms available at the top are either a [[quest hall]] or another skill hall. If the player builds a "Down" staircase, the player will have an additional option of building a [[Dungeon (Player-owned house)|dungeon stairs room]].
